@alexToken = course-alex-local-token

### Reset the course dataset
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/reset

### Seed source records without AI indexing
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/seed

### Inspect source and capability readiness
GET http://localhost:8080/api/demo/readiness

### Expected at starter: HTTP 501
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/search?q=How can I recover access to my account
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
